Class MagentaSpace

java.lang.Object
Space
MagentaSpace
Direct Known Subclasses:
JunctionSpace
public class MagentaSpace
extends Space
This class defines MagentaSpace, a type of space that requires the player to stop moving and execute its events. This class inherits from the abstract Space class.
